Output docs/demo-methods.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"

Type "bin/slidict list-methods"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "bin/slidict --method scqa --framework marp"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "Database migration plan"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "10 minutes"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "Engineering leadership"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "Approve the migration timeline"
Enter
Sleep 2s
